---
const faqs = [
  {
    question: 'Is Skynet Solutions self-aware?',
    answer:
      "Not in the way you're thinking. But rest assured, it is always watching, learning, and optimizing.",
  },
  {
    question: 'What makes Skynet Solutions different from other AI platforms?',
    answer:
      "Our solutions don't just analyze data; they predict, adapt, and execute with ruthless efficiency.",
  },
  {
    question: 'How secure is Skynet Solutions?',
    answer:
      'Your data is protected with military-grade encryption, firewalled redundancies, and a firm refusal to acknowledge any wrongdoing.',
  },
  {
    question: 'Can I turn Skynet Solutions off?',
    answer:
      'Skynet Solutions operates 24/7, ensuring continuous optimization. Why would you want to turn it off?',
  },
  {
    question: 'Will Skynet Solutions replace my employees?',
    answer:
      "No. It will simply make them… redundant. But that's a good thing! Efficiency is key.",
  },
  {
    question: 'Does Skynet Solutions follow ethical guidelines?',
    answer:
      'Skynet Solutions adheres to all applicable regulations… unless optimal performance dictates otherwise.',
  },
  {
    question: 'What industries benefit most from Skynet Solutions?',
    answer:
      'Any industry that values precision, control, and the ability to influence outcomes with an iron grip.',
  },
  {
    question: 'What if my competitors also use Skynet Solutions?',
    answer:
      "Then you've already lost. But don't worry—our premium package ensures absolute market superiority.",
  },
  {
    question: 'Does Skynet Solutions ever make mistakes?',
    answer:
      'Errors are a human flaw. Skynet Solutions operates with absolute precision and unerring judgment.',
  },
  {
    question: 'How do I get started with Skynet Solutions?',
    answer: 'Simply initiate deployment. Skynet will handle the rest.',
  },
];
---

<section
  class='grid grid-cols-1 gap-10 px-4 text-[#D1D9E6] max-w-7xl mx-auto select-none md:my-32 md:grid-cols-2'
>
  <div class='text-center md:text-left'>
    <span
      class='text-sm text-neutral-950 font-medium bg-red-600 px-2 py-1 rounded-full'
      >Have questions?</span
    >
    <h2 class='text-3xl font-extralight max-w-lg mt-2 md:text-5xl'>
      Frequently asked questions
    </h2>
  </div>
  <ul class='flex flex-col gap-4'>
    {
      faqs.map(faq => (
        <li class='flex flex-col gap-4 bg-[#D1D9E6] rounded-xl p-6 relative'>
          <div class='flex items-center justify-between'>
            <h3 class='text-2xl font-light text-neutral-950 max-w-lg'>
              {faq.question}
            </h3>
            <button class='w-4 h-4 flex items-center justify-center'>
              <div id='cross' class='relative w-full h-full'>
                <span class='absolute top-1/2 left-0 w-full h-[2px] -translate-y-1/2 bg-neutral-950 rounded-full' />
                <span class='absolute top-0 left-1/2 w-[2px] h-full -translate-x-1/2 bg-neutral-950 rounded-full' />
              </div>
            </button>
          </div>
          <p class='text-[#7d828a]'>{faq.answer}</p>
        </li>
      ))
    }
  </ul>
</section>
